          "sourceLabel": "en.wikipedia.org"
        },
        {
          "key": "year",
          "label": "原作年份",
          "value": "1875（首次出版）",
          "sourceUrl": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/To_God_Be_the_Glory",
          "sourceLabel": "en.wikipedia.org"
        },
        {
          "key": "themes",
          "label": "主題標籤",
          "value": "敬拜讚美、救恩",
          "sourceUrl": "https://www.hymnallibrary.org/hymns/to-god-be-the-glory/",
          "sourceLabel": "hymnallibrary.org"
        },
        {
          "key": "background",
          "label": "背景故事摘要",
          "value": "由著名聖詩作家 Fanny Crosby 作詞的基督教聖詩。歌曲主題是將一切榮耀歸於神，讚美祂藉耶穌基督所成就的救恩，並邀請信徒以喜樂和感恩回應神的恩典。此詩早期在英國已相當流行，然而在美國初期反應平平，鮮少被收入聖詩集。直到1954年，Billy Graham 團隊的領詩員 Cliff Barrows 將其用於倫敦佈道會，獲得熱烈迴響，其後迅速傳播至全球，成為現代教會最廣為收錄和傳唱的經典聖詩之一。",
          "sourceUrl": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/To_God_Be_the_Glory",
          "sourceLabel": "en.wikipedia.org"
        },
        {
          "key": "scripture",
          "label": "相關經文",
          "value": "加拉太書 1:4-5",
          "sourceUrl": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/To_God_Be_the_Glory",
          "sourceLabel": "en.wikipedia.org"
        }
      ],
