          "value": "1739",
          "sourceUrl": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/O_for_a_Thousand_Tongues_to_Sing",
          "sourceLabel": "en.wikipedia.org"
        },
        {
          "key": "themes",
          "label": "主題標籤",
          "value": "頌讚救主、恩典釋放、更新見證",
          "sourceUrl": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/O_for_a_Thousand_Tongues_to_Sing",
          "sourceLabel": "en.wikipedia.org"
        },
        {
          "key": "background",
          "label": "背景故事摘要",
          "value": "Charles Wesley在1738年患病期間的屬靈經歷。當時他因胸膜炎臥病在床，並對信仰充滿疑惑；然而在基督徒朋友的關懷、閱讀聖經及 Peter Boehler 的教導下，他重新經歷上帝的恩典與平安。為紀念信仰更新一周年，Charles Wesley 寫下這首讚美詩。其中著名歌詞「O for a thousand tongues to sing」靈感來自 Peter Boehler 的一句話，表達對上帝救恩與恩典無限的感恩和讚美。",
          "sourceUrl": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/O_for_a_Thousand_Tongues_to_Sing",
          "sourceLabel": "en.wikipedia.org"
        },
        {
          "key": "scripture",
